definition.text: A lot of surface covered, with a lot of room to grow.

paragraphs.text: The scope of this project is simply massive... it took me a little bit to get through some of the UI learning curves, and as I go through the tutorial even more, I'm finding that there are even larger pockets of massive scope that I didn't suspect that it would have. When I first came to SuperAlgos, I decided to try out other things because maybe it feels like this software is about the hardware race. At this point, I'm pretty sure that's wrong... but maybe later, I'll be able to change my review after I understand more SuperAlgos and get contribution tokens!
